      { val: "data-demographics", label: "I'm looking for viewer demographics data like age group and interests." }
    ],
    modal: true,
    attachment: true,
    poweredBy: false,
    instructions: "Need more data? Tell us what you're looking for and we'll get back to you with quickly."
  });
  $(function() {
    $('.open_hs_beacon').click(function() {
      HS.beacon.open();
      return false;
    });
  });
  // end Help Scout
</script>
